    "en": {
      "title": "Two killed in Katubedda shooting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two persons were killed in a shooting near the Bandaranaike Junction in Katubedda, Moratuwa a short while ago, police spokesman Nihal Thalduwa said.",
        "The deceased have been identified as Lilantha Kumara Silva alias Ukkuwa and Mohammad Uwais Mohammad Sakid Arpath.",
        "The shooting happened when they were traveling in a small van.",
        "One suspect was released from prison about a month ago.",
        "Police say they have received information about how the shooters arrived."
      ],
